Lonmin Marikana Output Halted by Community Protest, Business Report Says

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-08-24T05:49:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-24/lonmin-marikana-output-halted-by-community-protest-business-report-says.html
Production at two shafts of  Lonmin
Plc (LMI) ’s Marikana platinum mine was halted by protests from nearby
community members who are demanding that the company employ its
residents, Business Report said, citing Bernard Mokwena,
Lonmin’s vice-president of external affairs.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  